- Implimneting Scanner
- Removing unused varibiles
- getting rid of useless methods(CompareTo)
- Use factory for monsters
- use Stratagy for heros
- Hero and monster are concrete classes.
- Its easy to add between the diffrenet behavoir heroes and monsters and each one will works well.
- Each hero has HeroBehavior and each Monster has his own MonsterBehavior.
- HeroFactory responsible for adding new heroes.
- MonsterFactory will be resposible for adding new monster everytime with their attack style.
- I have applied a Strategy Pattern for Hero so each hero will have diffrentes behavior, I used interface so we can switch.
- Also I have applied Strategy Pattern for Monster so each monster will have his own behave.
